title: EXTRA: Trump Criticism of McCain in 2016
itunes:title: EXTRA: Trump Criticism of McCain in 2016
description:
Kevin discusses criticism of 2020 Democratic presidential frontrunner Joe Biden by White House Counselor Kellyanne Conway with Kevin Walling, Democratic Strategist at HG Creative Media and Rick Tyler Republican strategist and Communications Director for the Ted Cruz 2016 Presidential Campaign recounts campaign strategy after candidate Donald Trump criticized war hero Senator John McCain in Iowa in 2016.
